1
00:00:00,253 --> 00:00:01,973
(Match to Marry: With parents is...)

2
00:00:02,753 --> 00:00:04,460
(back for season 2.)

3
00:00:04,544 --> 00:00:06,747
- She's gorgeous.
- Is this a beauty contest?

4
00:00:06,831 --> 00:00:07,847
He's handsome.

5
00:00:07,931 --> 00:00:10,760
I'm done dating. What I want
is a marriage.

6
00:00:11,248 --> 00:00:12,648
You're my dream type.

7
00:00:13,221 --> 00:00:15,835
The world started to feel a bit brighter
because of you.

8
00:00:16,334 --> 00:00:18,667
It's hard to overlook a person's education
and job.

9
00:00:18,765 --> 00:00:20,715
Mothers don't like it
when they are too young.

10
00:00:20,866 --> 00:00:22,246
The age gap...

11
00:00:22,399 --> 00:00:24,472
It really hit me that we had
very different spiritual perspectives.

12
00:00:24,556 --> 00:00:26,506
I've seen quite a few couples
divorce over religion.

13
00:00:26,590 --> 00:00:28,457
Busan is just a quick KTX ride away.

14
00:00:28,540 --> 00:00:30,359
How could he leave all of that behind
and come here?

15
00:00:30,662 --> 00:00:32,695
- And then to send you far away again...
- I'm not letting you go that far.

16
00:00:32,779 --> 00:00:33,795
Did you hear that?

17
00:00:33,879 --> 00:00:36,988
- This is my future son-in-law.
- Mom, you're not the one marrying him.

18
00:00:37,072 --> 00:00:38,768
It's a no from me.

19
00:00:38,852 --> 00:00:41,758
I repeatedly chose her.
While you never once chose her.

20
00:00:41,842 --> 00:00:43,772
- Leave it, I'll take care of it.
- What did you say?

21
00:00:43,856 --> 00:00:45,426
I was pretty shocked by it.

22
00:00:45,510 --> 00:00:47,652
(As the turmoil of feelings deepens...)

23
00:00:47,736 --> 00:00:49,700
(There is another surprise
waiting for them.)

24
00:00:49,784 --> 00:00:50,807
Open it.

25
00:00:50,891 --> 00:00:53,230
(Another family member entering?)

26
00:00:53,314 --> 00:00:54,400
Dad!

27
00:00:54,487 --> 00:00:56,527
(Match to Marry 2)
